description: [``botocore``] This change adds support for tagging Chatbot configurations.
[``botocore``] Added DeletionMode FORCE_DELETE_STACK for deleting a stack that is stuck in DELETE_FAILED state due to resource deletion failure.
[``botocore``] This release includes feature to import customer's asymmetric (RSA, ECC and SM2) and HMAC keys into KMS in China.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for enabling or disabling a data source configured as part of Zero-ETL integration with Amazon S3, by setting its status.
[``botocore``] You can now use Security Lake to collect web ACL traffic data.
